info.title: XigniteNAVs
info.description: This web service provides latest NAV information for all funds.

post.description: This operation returns the latest NAV information for a funds.
This operation returns the latest NAV information for a list of funds.
This operation returns a list of funds descreptive information.

GetLatestNAVOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetLatestNAVResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetLatestNAVResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:Fund>
     <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
     <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
     <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
     <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
     <tns:FundName>string</tns:FundName>
     <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
     <tns:CUSIP>string</tns:CUSIP>
     <tns:CIK>string</tns:CIK>
     <tns:ISIN>string</tns:ISIN>
     <tns:Valoren>string</tns:Valoren>
     <tns:Market>string</tns:Market>
     <tns:MarketIdentificationCode>string</tns:MarketIdentificationCode>
     <tns:MostLiquidExchange><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:MostLiquidExchange>
    </tns:Fund>
    <tns:NAV>
     <tns:Date>string</tns:Date>
     <tns:Time>string</tns:Time>
     <tns:UTCOffset><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:UTCOffset>
     <tns:Open><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Open>
     <tns:High><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:High>
     <tns:Low><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Low>
     <tns:Last><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Last>
     <tns:Close><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Close>
     <tns:PreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PreviousClose>
     <tns:ChangeFromOpen><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ChangeFromOpen>
     <tns:PercentChangeFromOpen><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PercentChangeFromOpen>
     <tns:ChangeFromPreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ChangeFromPreviousClose>
     <tns:PercentChangeFromPreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PercentChangeFromPreviousClose>
     <tns:Yield><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Yield>
    </tns:NAV>
   </tns:GetLatestNAVResult>
  </tns:GetLatestNAVResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
